'''渡邊大佑'''（1974年3月11日—）日本[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]][[編劇|編劇]]，就職於[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]。他最知名的作品是[[電子角色扮演遊戲|電子角色扮演遊戲]]系列[[最終幻想|最終幻想]]和[[動作角色扮演遊戲|動作角色扮演遊戲]]系列[[王國之心|王國之心]]。

== 最終幻想作品 ==

《[[最終幻想X|最終幻想X]]》是渡邊第一個擔任編劇的[[最終幻想|最終幻想]]遊戲<ref name="ultimaniaomega">{{cite book | title=Final Fantasy X Ultimania Omega | publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] | pages=191–193, 476 | author=Studio BentStuff | language=ja}}</ref>。2004年11月，他加入《[[最終幻想XII|最終幻想XII]]》開發團隊<ref>{{cite book | year=2006 | editor=Studio BentStuff | title=Final Fantasy XII Scenario Ultimania | url=http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/7273/37526950.jpg | publisher=Square Enix | language=ja | isbn=4-7575-1696-7 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724182745/http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/7273/37526950.jpg | archivedate=2011-07-24 }}</ref>，团队原編劇[[松野泰己|松野泰己]]因疾病原因於2005年退出創作<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web|last=Niizumi|first=Hirohiko|title=FFXII producer steps down|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/news/2005/08/01/news_6130121.html|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=20 March 2011|date=1 August 2005|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130102210427/http://uk.gamespot.com/news/2005/08/01/news_6130121.html|archivedate=2013年1月2日}}</ref>。

《最終幻想XII》的的共同監製[[皆川裕史|皆川裕史]]稱，為讓遊戲趕上發行日期，渡邊的很多故事創意不得不遺憾的取消<ref name="dvd">{{cite web|title=Video interview with FINAL FANTASY XII Directors|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EYIzjBbO2FQ|work=FINAL FANTASY XII Collector's Edition Bonus DVD|publisher=[[Square_Enix_Co.,_Ltd|Square Enix Co., Ltd]]|accessdate=8 April 2011|date=31 October 2006|quote=Hiroshi Minagawa: In the course of development, Jun Akiyama and Daisuke Watanabe came up with many ideas but ultimately we had to abandon many of them. I'd heard their original ideas and I wish we could have included them all. Once we began development and many of the systems were in place, the team had many progressive ideas. It was the most enjoyable part of the project. But as we approached the project's end, I had to point out features we had to drop in order for the game to be finished. Which is unfortunate, since I'm sure people would have enjoyed the game that much more if we could have left all our original ideas in.|archive-date=2013-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206221711/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EYIzjBbO2FQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年3月，在[[野岛一成|野岛一成]]和[[鳥山求|鳥山求]]分別為《[[最終幻想XIII|最終幻想XIII]]》創作神话和劇情後，渡邊也加入了開發團隊。鳥山交給了他前8章的情節大綱，並要求他添写具體情節並修正所有銜接桥段。渡邊決定該如何顯示鳥山的過場動畫構思，為強調故事表達，他改写了剧本並調整了个别角色的個性<ref>{{cite book |title=Final Fantasy XIII Scenario Ultimania |publisher=Studio Bentstuff |location=Tokyo |isbn=4-7575-2775-6 |pages=388–390 |language=ja |date=2010-02-01}}</ref>。

